programme.title: Inside Claridge's
programme.desc: Documentary series following a year behind the scenes at five-star luxury hotel Claridge's, following both the staff and their guests. Since its opening in 1854, Claridge's has become famous for its art deco interiors and its traditional service. Many of its members of staff have been employed there for decades, and their presence gives guests a sense of continuity whilst the interiors give a feeling of living in another age. Regular visitors to the hotel include the Crown Prince of Yugoslavia, who returns to stay in the suite where he was born back in 1945.
